query:
SELECT i.id, i.business_name, i.contact_name, i.email, i.status, i.preview_token, i.created_at 
FROM intakes i 
WHERE i.email = 'aboveboardmillwork@gmail.com' 
ORDER BY i.created_at DESC 
LIMIT 5;
